OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Ffine, warm and sunny evening in all
OL,7,Fareas then a dry night with some long
OL,8,Fclear spells. Clouding over by morning.
OL,9,
OL,10,CSaturday:FA dry day. A rather cloudy
OL,11,Fstart then the cloud breaking up to
OL,12,Fallow some sunny spells again.
OL,13,
OL,14,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,15,Fwith sunny periods on Sunday, warm
OL,16,Fwith light winds. More cloud at times
OL,17,Fon Monday and Tuesday but still dry
OL,18,Fwith some sunny intervals.
